glass bottles. The sprayer version is easy to hold and spray. The sprayer is top notch even better than I was expecting . I filled one with my zero odor and I get a great fine mist . No drips or wet floor. I took the sticker off the plastic bottle and put it on my glass bottle. It came with a chalkboard type label, but I wanted my lable on this one. Review Title: Fine mist out of pretty bottle Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Empty Brown Glass Spray Bottles2-Pack, Refillable 16 oz Containers for Essential Oils, Cleaning Products, Aromatherapy, Misting Plants, or Cooking - Reliable Sprayer with Mist and Stream Settings Review Date: 2020/09/07 Store: Cherry Average Rating: 3.7 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Cherry', 'Material': 'Glass', 'Capacity': '16 Ounces', 'Number of Items': '2', 'Product Care Instructions': 'Hand Wash Only', 'Package Dimensions': '9.09 x 6.46 x 3.35 inches; 4.94 Ounces', 'UPC': '791523234187'} Review Text: Ive been ordering glass bottles and moving my products into them. I get refill size and transfer. These 2 spray bottles were a little thinne not bad, but still sturdy enough and the spray top where the sprayer is spins loosely 360 degrees. ?? I just filled it with my gallon of orange cleaner and I had to take off the sprayer and toss it in the garbage! The flaw is the spinning sprayer that allowed my expensive orange cleaner to pour out of the top all around the nozzle. cheaply made but all in all a good glass bottle with a terrible srayer . If you just need a bottle with a screw top your good. If you have a different sprayer you can take off a plastic bottle great. Thats what I did. I took the label off my orange cleaner and stuck it on this bottle and it looks so nice. So my sprayer and label made a great usable bottle. Review Title: Needs a different sprayer that works Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: [Marshique] Patented Eyelash Dryer - Extension & Lift/Perm Care Mascara Dry No Damage Curl USB Rechargeable Review Date: 2020/11/07 Store: Marshique Average Rating: 2.6 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Marshique', 'Handle Type': 'Massage Handle', 'Operation Mode': 'Automatic'} Review Text: I love that this handy dandy eyelash dryer is rechargeable. So when I received this I was sceptical. So I put my mascara on put this at the base of my lash and turned it on while pushing my eyelash up gently. Warm air gently dried them curled up. It shut off when finished. No hard squeeze with an eyelash curler needed ! This tool gently does the job. I love this tool. Easy to hold and use. Review Title: It's rechargeable , gently dries and curls lashes Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Make-up Organizers Storage Cosmetic Organizer Display Case Dustproof Storage Box Waterproof Holder Used for Bathroom w/Handle Christmas Gift 12"L x 16"H White Review Date: 2020/11/30 Store: LOMANTOWN Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Mounting Type Tabletop Mount': '', '': 'Unit Count 1.00 Count', 'Specific Uses For Product': 'Makeup Organizer,Cosmetic Organizer,Bathroom', 'Material': 'Plastic', 'Special Feature': 'Waterproof,Durable', 'Brand': 'LOMANTOWN', 'Package Type': 'Standard Packaging', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Package Dimensions': '17.25 x 13.25 x 10.35 inches; 5.6 Pounds'} Review Text: This is a very nice case, as you can see in the picture it holds full size items. I haven't decided what all I want to put in it but when I do it holds plenty. It could be used for different purposes. Review Title: Well made ,multi uses Rating: 5.0 --------------------------------------------------

- **Skin Care:** Interest in anti-aging and revitalizing creams, favoring earthy scents over synthetic fragrances.

- **Hair Care:** Focus on solutions for thinning and greying hair, with an appreciation for products that effectively blend and cover imperfections.

- **Home & Storage:** Strong inclination towards eco-friendly and aesthetically pleasing storage solutions, particularly glass containers for multipurpose uses, indicating a preference for sustainability and functionality.

- **Product Quality Concerns:** Experiences reveal a critical approach towards product efficacy and packaging quality, with multiple mentions of product effectiveness and durability.

- **Utility & Organization:** Preference for practical, well-designed items that simplify and organize personal care routines while maintaining a tidiness in living spaces.

Overall, the individual showcases a balance between beauty enhancements and home organization, with a consistent focus on natural ingredients and efficiency in product design.

target_interaction.title: Works but not gentle
target_interaction.text:
This face mask didnt work like what I see in demonstrations on YouTube. It work but much more slowly. It burned
around the sides of my nose down by my mouth and after a couple of days made scabby tissue ,it was pretty raw. I guess I have sensitive skin. I can use it but will avoid this super tender area. It worked to lighten the top of the nose blackheads. I definitely think 2 times a week is the max for using to avoid my issue.
